The Debian Package platina-linux-kernel
----------------------------

This package builds the latest kernel as a debian package, and builds
a metapackage that points to this version.

If you install the metapackage, you will get automatic kernel updates.

If you install the explicit versioned package, you will not get automatic
updates.

If you install both, you will get automatic updates, but old versions
will not be suggested for autoremoval. 

